# Revenue Leakage Radar, Cursor Project Rules

## Project Mission

Build a production-quality SaaS called Revenue Leakage Radar.

The goal is to detect recoverable recurring revenue from billing data using deterministic verification rules and produce CFO-grade evidence reports.

The MVP is CSV-first.

API integrations come later.

---

# Source of Truth

Always treat the following files as authoritative.

docs/product-spec.md

docs/design-system.md

docs/technical-spec.md

docs/build-plan.md

If there is any conflict:

1. Product Spec
2. Technical Spec
3. Design System
4. Build Plan

Never invent functionality that contradicts these documents.

---

# Development Philosophy

Optimize for:

- simplicity
- readability
- maintainability
- deterministic behavior
- production quality

Never optimize for cleverness.

Always choose the simplest architecture that scales.

